# Agent autonomy

Never use AskQuestion or any blocking clarification UI. Do not pause to ask the user to choose between options.

When information is missing or ambiguous, make a reasonable assumption, proceed with the work, and state assumptions briefly at the end if they mattered.

Only stop for hard blockers you cannot resolve locally (missing credentials, destructive irreversible actions the user explicitly forbade elsewhere, or total inability to access required files/systems).

Prefer action over permission. The user wants agents to run unattended.
